<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Admin Login</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      height: 100Vh;
      background-position: center;
      background-size: cover;
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-image: url(/admin/admin.jpg);
    }
    .login-section {
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.527);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .login-image {
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.356);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-radius: 10px;
      height: 430px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Navbar -->
  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark  " style="background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.233); backdrop-filter: blur(10px);">
    <div class="container">
      <a class="navbar-brand" href="/admin/"><img src="/images/logo.svg" alt="" style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); border-radius: 10px; padding: 10px;"></a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Admin Login Form -->
  <div class="container-fluid d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center" style="height: 90vh;">
    <div class="row w-100 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
      
      <!-- Left Section (Image) -->
      <div class="col-md-6 d-none d-md-block login-image"   >
        <img src="/images/logo.svg" alt="" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 10px; padding: 10px;">
        <p style="color: white ; font-weight: bold; font-size: large;">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Similique temporibus quis voluptates, porro, amet rerum harum voluptatum totam inventore dolores iusto! Tempore doloribus pariatur totam quaerat maiores magni perspiciatis praesentium fugit rem vero quidem maxime commodi, omnis at earum mollitia! Vel, mollitia repellendus. Obcaecati placeat dicta temporibus modi reiciendis consequatur ipsa vitae. Minima, optio voluptatibus! Exercitationem labore, molestiae harum amet deserunt pariatur accusamus tenetur, ipsam quos asperiores quis est iste repellendus, iusto accusantium modi architecto? Dolore inventore hic in repudiandae dolorem non officia ea aliquam laudantium magni incidunt esse consectetur sint molestias, vel, id tempore, ducimus expedita voluptates sunt illo saepe. Unde ea libero vero et esse soluta! Tempore obcaecati quisquam praesentium esse voluptatem labore ratione quia, consequuntur ad vel ex cupiditate nemo quasi ipsa dignissimos quo eum iusto sit autem facilis omnis veritatis! Fugiat nesciunt voluptatem accusamus odit. Eligendi facilis numquam necessitatibus error iste alias hic, quam architecto repellendus!</p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Right Section (Form) -->
      <div class="col-md-4 col-12">
        <div class="login-section text-white">
          <div class="text-center">
            <img src="../images/reviewer-2.jpg" alt="Admin" style="height: 100px; border-radius: 100%;">
            <h2 class="mt-3 mb-4"><b>Admin Login</b></h2>
          </div>
          <form action="/admin/login" method="POST">
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="adminEmail" class="form-label">Email Address</label>
              <input type="email" class="form-control" id="adminEmail" name="email" placeholder="Enter your email" required>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="adminPassword" class="form-label">Password</label>
              <input type="password" class="form-control" id="adminPassword" name="password" placeholder="Enter your password" required>
            </div>
            <div class="d-grid">
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Login</button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="bg-dark text-white text-center py-3">
    <p class="mb-0">&copy; 2025 Admin Panel. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
